                       Angular front end technology
basic

1.create priject-ng new project name
2. to run project  -  ng serve
3. to generate component - ng g c component-name

             basic concept

 1.module - to import libraries root module- appmodule

 2.component- to generate ts,html,css,root component-appcomponent

3. data binding - sharing data with in component
      
      3.1 one way binding - only single direction
                (ts-component,html-view)

         3.1.1  component to view

              3.1.1.1 string interpolation -{{variable name}}
              
              3.1.1.2 property binding - [tag attribute]="class-property


         3.1.2 view to component
          
           3.1.2.1 event binding - {event-name}="function call"

           3.1.2.2 event binding using sevent - {event-name}="function call"

           


